1 (F) (1) A CEMETERY OWNER SHALL, IN CONSULTATION WITH THE
2 DIRECTOR, DEVELOP A PRESERVATION PLAN FOR A CEMETERY THAT THE
3 CEMETERY OWNER INTENDS TO SELL OR TRANSFER.
4 (2) IN DEVELOPING THE PRESERVATION PLAN UNDER PARAGRAPH
5 (1) OF THIS SUBSECTION, THE CEMETERY OWNER SHALL COMPLY WITH SUBSECTION
