17 UNDER THIS SECTION, THE CEMETERY OWNER SHALL PROVIDE PUBLIC NOTICE OF
18 THE CEMETERY OWNER’S INTENT TO SELL OR TRANSFER THE CEMETERY BY:
19 (I) PUBLISHING NOTICE OF THE SALE OR TRANSFER IN A
20 NEWSPAPER OF GENERAL CIRCULATION IN THE COUNTY WHERE THE CEMETERY IS
