1 (K) AN ACTION MAY BE BROUGHT IN ACCORDANCE WITH THE MARYLAND
2 RULES AND A COURT MAY PASS JUDGMENT REGARDING THE SALE OF A BURIAL
3 GROUND FOR ANOTHER PURPOSE IF ANY PARTY DISPUTES THE DIRECTOR’S
